---
import Layout from '../Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="BLACKPINK - All The News">

    <main>
        <section class="news-section fade-in">
            <h1 class="page-title">Latest News</h1>
            <p class="page-subtitle">Stay Updated with BLACKPINK</p>
        </section>

        <section class="blog-container">
            <article class="blog-post fade-in-up">
                <div class="blog-image">
                    <div class="placeholder-image" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff1744 0%, #f50057 100%);">
                        <span class="image-text">CONCERT</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="blog-content">
                    <div class="blog-top">
                        <span class="blog-date">March 15, 2025</span>
                        <span class="blog-category">Tour</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="blog-title">BORN PINK World Tour: Record-Breaking Success</h2>
                    <div class="blog-text">
                        <p>
                            BLACKPINK's BORN PINK World Tour has officially concluded, marking one of the most 
                            successful concert tours in K-pop history. Spanning over 36 cities across Asia, North 
                            America, Europe, Oceania, and the Middle East, the tour attracted over 1.8 million fans 
                            worldwide. The production showcased spectacular stage designs, cutting-edge visual effects, 
                            and unforgettable performances of both classic hits and recent releases.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Each concert featured a carefully curated setlist that took fans on an emotional journey 
                            through BLACKPINK's discography. From the explosive energy of "DDU-DU DDU-DU" to the 
                            emotional depth of "Hard to Love," every performance demonstrated the group's artistic 
                            growth and unparalleled stage presence. The tour's finale in Seoul was particularly 
                            memorable, with special guest appearances and a heartfelt message from the members to 
                            their devoted BLINK fanbase, expressing gratitude for years of unwavering support and love.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/blog/first" class="read-more">Read Full Article →</a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="blog-post fade-in-up">
                <div class="blog-image">
                    <div class="placeholder-image" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e91e63 0%, #c2185b 100%);">
                        <span class="image-text">MUSIC VIDEO</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="blog-content">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span class="blog-date">February 28, 2025</span>
                        <span class="blog-category">Release</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="blog-title">New Single "Shut Down" Breaks YouTube Records</h2>
                    <div class="blog-text">
                        <p>
                            BLACKPINK's latest single "Shut Down" has shattered multiple YouTube records within hours 
                            of its release. The music video garnered over 100 million views in just 48 hours, making it 
                            the fastest K-pop group music video to achieve this milestone. The song's bold hip-hop sound 
                            and striking visuals have captivated fans globally, with the distinctive sampling of 
                            Paganini's "La Campanella" adding a classical twist to their signature style.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            The music video, filmed in luxurious locations around the world, features the members in 
                            stunning haute couture fashion, showcasing their evolution as global fashion icons. Choreography 
                            highlights include powerful group formations and individual solo sections that allow each member 
                            to shine. Critics have praised the song's confident lyrics and production quality, noting how 
                            BLACKPINK continues to push boundaries while maintaining their unique identity. The track has 
                            already topped iTunes charts in over 70 countries and continues to dominate streaming platforms.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/blog/second" class="read-more">Read Full Article →</a>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="blog-post fade-in-up">
                <div class="blog-image">
                    <div class="placeholder-image" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f50057 0%, #880e4f 100%);">
                        <span class="image-text">COMEBACK</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="blog-content">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span class="blog-date">January 10, 2025</span>
                        <span class="blog-category">Announcement</span>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="blog-title">BLACKPINK Announces 2025 Comeback Plans</h2>
                    <div class="blog-text">
                        <p>
                            YG Entertainment has officially confirmed that BLACKPINK will be making their highly 
                            anticipated comeback in 2025 with a brand new album. After focusing on individual solo 
                            activities and the massive success of their BORN PINK World Tour, the four members are 
                            reuniting to create fresh music that promises to showcase their artistic maturity and 
                            evolution. The announcement sent shockwaves through the K-pop community, trending worldwide 
                            within minutes and generating millions of excited reactions from BLINK across the globe.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            According to sources close to the group, the upcoming album will feature collaborations 
                            with renowned international producers and will explore diverse musical genres while 
                            maintaining BLACKPINK's signature sound. The members have been actively involved in the 
                            creative process, from songwriting to concept development, ensuring that this comeback 
                            truly represents their collective vision. Alongside the album release, a series of special 
                            performances and fan engagement activities are being planned. Industry experts predict this 
                            comeback could set new records and further cement BLACKPINK's position as global superstars.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/blog/third" class="read-more">Read Full Article →</a>
                </div>
            </article>
        </section>

        <section class="news-section fade-in-up">
            <h2 class="section-title">Want to See Tour Dates?</h2>
            <p class="news-text">Check out our dedicated tour page for all upcoming concerts and events!</p>
            <a href="/tour" class="button">View Tour Dates →</a>
        </section>
    </main>

</Layout>


